WEBVTT

01:37.940 --> 01:40.630
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.289 --> 01:43.600
[Episode 1]

01:44.150 --> 01:46.000
There exists a race
of War Demons in the world

01:46.000 --> 01:48.479
who defy the laws of heaven
and disrespect the gods,

01:48.479 --> 01:50.200
thus incurring divine abhorrence.

01:50.200 --> 01:52.560
The gods cast 5 curses upon them,

01:53.120 --> 01:55.590
including hot-blooded mania,
inability to feel pain,

01:55.590 --> 01:57.560
no rest, no colors to see,

01:58.039 --> 02:00.310
and tasting everything like rot.

02:01.070 --> 02:03.350
This divine punishment was to last
a thousand years,

02:03.350 --> 02:04.790
but as the term neared its end,

02:04.790 --> 02:08.050
the heavenly ladder was severed
and the gods disappeared.

02:08.110 --> 02:10.229
For the sake of salvation, the War Demons

02:10.229 --> 02:14.290
sought the sacred seed of the Jianmu Tree
to rebuild the heavenly ladder.

02:14.530 --> 02:17.250
However,
the Jianmu Tree was a divine creation

02:17.480 --> 02:20.079
that required over ten thousand years
to mature.

02:20.079 --> 02:23.710
The War Demons planned to sacrifice
half of all living beings

02:24.150 --> 02:26.410
to accelerate the divine tree's growth.

02:26.560 --> 02:28.420
This act violated heaven's laws,

02:28.520 --> 02:31.800
causing humans and the Youhu (Fox) Clan
to join forces against them.

02:31.800 --> 02:32.400
In the end,

02:32.910 --> 02:35.430
under the leadership
of the Youhu Clan's High Priest Yuan Zhong

02:35.430 --> 02:37.400
and the human immortal sects,

02:37.710 --> 02:40.310
they completely exterminated
the War Demons.

02:41.420 --> 02:45.880
The Great Dao holds 50 paths, while heaven
manifests 49, leaving one for humans.

02:46.000 --> 02:48.079
If War Demons
wish to be reborn as humans,

02:48.079 --> 02:51.720
ascending to heaven to seek the gods is
not necessarily their only choice.

02:51.720 --> 02:53.440
With their skin peeled off,
their flesh carved off,

02:52.490 --> 02:56.400
[Prison, Wei County]

02:53.470 --> 02:55.550
their bones scraped clean, their blood
renewed, and their hearts gouged out,

02:55.550 --> 02:57.280
they could be reborn as humans.

02:57.870 --> 02:59.870
Yet these five trials are perilous.

02:59.910 --> 03:03.240
War Demons must form blood pacts
with their closest kin

03:03.430 --> 03:05.470
so that when near death,

03:05.800 --> 03:08.000
they might grasp
a silver lining of survival.

03:06.280 --> 03:08.300
[Lu Huai]

03:17.840 --> 03:19.770
Are you the esteemed Immortal Xin?

03:19.780 --> 03:23.560
[Xin Mei from Xin Xie Manor]

03:20.960 --> 03:22.190
I'm too shallow in cultivation

03:22.190 --> 03:23.850
to bear the title "Immortal."

03:24.560 --> 03:25.960
You're being too modest.

03:26.590 --> 03:28.110
Are you a constable here?

03:28.190 --> 03:28.560
Yes.

03:28.710 --> 03:29.510
[Chu Ying]

03:28.870 --> 03:29.680
I am Chu Ying.

03:30.190 --> 03:31.310
Did Madam Song tell you

03:31.310 --> 03:32.510
about the situation?

03:33.560 --> 03:35.290
But she didn't go into details.

03:35.520 --> 03:36.120
It's okay.

03:36.310 --> 03:37.370
Let's talk inside.

03:37.520 --> 03:37.980
Please.

03:38.370 --> 03:44.390
[County Prison]

03:41.680 --> 03:43.710
How long have you been back, Immortal Xin?

03:43.710 --> 03:44.440
Just a while.

03:44.800 --> 03:46.380
Are you back specifically for this matter

03:46.380 --> 03:47.640
or for other business?

03:48.430 --> 03:51.720
For both personal and official affairs.
I'm handling this along the way.

03:51.720 --> 03:53.120
You've been away from home
for so long, Immortal Xin.

03:53.120 --> 03:55.240
You must have loads of things
to attend to.

03:55.240 --> 03:55.960
If there's anything

03:55.960 --> 03:57.020
I can help you with,

03:57.560 --> 03:59.360
I'll be at your service anytime.

03:59.470 --> 04:00.800
You don't need to go this far.

04:00.800 --> 04:01.800
It's my pleasure.

04:02.240 --> 04:03.840
Now that the War Demons are all extinct,

04:03.840 --> 04:05.800
in terms of status and prestige
in this world,

04:05.800 --> 04:07.800
apart from the Youhu Clan's immortals,

04:07.800 --> 04:09.800
no one can beat cultivators like you.

04:09.800 --> 04:10.960
Even emperors, generals,

04:10.960 --> 04:12.560
and ministers are no match for you.

04:12.560 --> 04:13.620
We're all the same.

04:13.700 --> 04:14.070
No,

04:14.520 --> 04:15.250
not the same.

04:15.280 --> 04:16.810
You're totally different.

04:19.070 --> 04:20.240
It's a bit rough here.

04:20.240 --> 04:22.070
Please don't mind, Immortal Xin.

04:22.070 --> 04:22.870
Mind the step.

04:26.750 --> 04:27.240
Lu,

04:28.040 --> 04:29.240
Immortal Xin is here.

04:31.440 --> 04:32.700
Immortal Xin is so kind

04:32.950 --> 04:34.750
that she even brought you a gift.

04:35.630 --> 04:38.090
And it's Song's pastries
from Fuxiang Lane.

04:40.040 --> 04:41.240
These aren't for him.

04:41.360 --> 04:42.490
They're for my aunt.

04:42.750 --> 04:44.040
The elderly lady is advanced in years

04:44.040 --> 04:44.920
and has poor teeth.

04:44.920 --> 04:46.409
This shop's pastries are soft and tender,

04:46.409 --> 04:47.680
perfect for the elderly.

04:47.680 --> 04:48.920
And they're only for sale in the morning.

04:48.920 --> 04:50.580
They're already sold out now.

04:53.000 --> 04:53.770
If you want them,

04:53.770 --> 04:55.770
I'll bring you some next time I come.

04:57.390 --> 04:58.050
Please sit.

05:04.870 --> 05:05.310
This is

05:05.720 --> 05:08.650
Xin Mei from the Xin Xie Manor,
known as Immortal Xin.

05:08.750 --> 05:10.630
You know the Xin Xie Manor, don't you?

05:10.630 --> 05:11.920
One of the twelve greatest immortal sects.

05:11.920 --> 05:14.560
They once followed
the Youhu Clan's High Priest.

05:14.560 --> 05:15.830
In the Battle of Pinghu,

05:15.830 --> 05:18.070
they wiped out the entire War Demon Clan.

05:18.070 --> 05:19.160
The sect leader, Xin Xiong, is

05:19.160 --> 05:20.720
a cultivator
in the Great Completion Realm.

05:20.720 --> 05:21.240
Now,

05:21.310 --> 05:22.680
the sect has only two disciples,

05:22.680 --> 05:24.510
and Immortal Xin is one of them.

05:25.190 --> 05:25.720
How's it?

05:26.030 --> 05:27.160
Impressive, right?

05:27.310 --> 05:28.310
So she's a master.

05:28.720 --> 05:29.850
Indeed impressive.

05:30.800 --> 05:31.430
This is

05:31.630 --> 05:32.750
Lu Huai,

05:32.920 --> 05:33.560
Lord Lu.

05:34.190 --> 05:36.520
He's the former magistrate of Wei County,

05:36.870 --> 05:37.830
with a military background,

05:37.830 --> 05:38.830
battle-hardened for years.

05:38.830 --> 05:40.830
His military achievements were earned
on the battlefield.

05:40.830 --> 05:43.240
A genuine case
of promotion through credit.

05:43.240 --> 05:44.040
Now...

05:48.800 --> 05:49.480
Now,

05:49.720 --> 05:50.390
as you know.

05:51.120 --> 05:51.800
Anyway,

05:52.120 --> 05:53.750
this is your big moment.

05:53.830 --> 05:55.960
How about I let you two talk privately?

05:57.720 --> 05:58.270
Okay.

05:58.720 --> 05:59.240
Good,

05:59.440 --> 06:00.320
thank you, sir.

06:00.950 --> 06:02.000
My pleasure.

06:02.090 --> 06:03.420
Take your time talking.

06:03.480 --> 06:04.480
I'll step outside.

06:04.480 --> 06:06.080
Call me if you need anything.

06:09.680 --> 06:10.390
Xin Mei?

06:12.120 --> 06:13.320
How do you write them?

06:28.000 --> 06:30.430
Xin Mei,
with this "mei" that means riverbank?

06:30.430 --> 06:32.600
I thought it was the "mei" from "eyebrow."

06:32.600 --> 06:33.730
They sound similar.

06:35.920 --> 06:37.070
You look very young

06:37.270 --> 06:38.070
and pretty,

06:38.480 --> 06:39.880
and you're a cultivator.

06:39.920 --> 06:40.980
Why are you willing

06:41.120 --> 06:42.520
to marry someone like me?

06:43.159 --> 06:44.270
Marry a prisoner

06:45.000 --> 06:46.930
who's about to be executed like me?

06:47.720 --> 06:48.270
I am

06:49.680 --> 06:50.390
jinxed.

06:52.070 --> 06:52.830
Jinxed?

06:53.040 --> 06:54.159
When I was just born,

06:54.159 --> 06:55.190
the fortune teller said

06:55.190 --> 06:57.750
I have a fate of widowhood,
cursed to bring misfortune to my husband.

06:57.750 --> 06:58.630
When I was little, my family

06:58.630 --> 07:00.040
arranged a childhood engagement for me.

07:00.040 --> 07:01.040
But within a year,

07:01.360 --> 07:03.160
that family's child died young.

07:03.720 --> 07:05.120
Later, I joined an immortal sect,

07:05.120 --> 07:05.920
and my master tried to set me up

07:05.920 --> 07:07.830
with a fellow disciple
from Zigai Mountain.

07:07.830 --> 07:09.360
But less than six months
after our engagement,

07:09.360 --> 07:11.750
that disciple lost control
and went mad during cultivation

07:11.750 --> 07:12.630
and died.

07:13.800 --> 07:14.920
So a master told me

07:15.190 --> 07:16.560
I must marry 3 times

07:16.800 --> 07:19.060
to dissolve the deadly energy in my fate.

07:19.270 --> 07:20.040
So...

07:23.870 --> 07:24.830
You have a crush?

07:25.870 --> 07:27.130
You want to use my death

07:27.360 --> 07:29.390
to remove the deadly energy
from your fate,

07:29.390 --> 07:30.850
so you and your beloved one

07:31.070 --> 07:32.600
can lead a happy life together,

07:32.600 --> 07:33.040
right?

07:34.120 --> 07:34.600
I...

07:36.920 --> 07:38.520
I am indeed a perfect choice.

07:40.630 --> 07:41.490
What about you?

07:41.920 --> 07:43.580
Why do you want to get married?

07:45.720 --> 07:46.920
All my family is gone.

07:47.390 --> 07:48.590
I'm about to die, too.

07:48.680 --> 07:50.070
I've never gotten married.

07:50.070 --> 07:51.510
I'm afraid that after I die,

07:51.510 --> 07:52.840
no one will remember me,

07:53.000 --> 07:54.260
and during festivals,

07:54.430 --> 07:56.890
no one will burn incense
or offerings for me.

08:00.040 --> 08:00.630
So?

08:01.720 --> 08:02.390
What?

08:03.270 --> 08:04.530
What do you think of me?

08:04.680 --> 08:06.280
Do I meet your requirements?

08:10.510 --> 08:11.750
You know very well

08:12.560 --> 08:13.760
that it's just a deal.

08:14.240 --> 08:15.040
You can go back

08:15.060 --> 08:16.560
and think it over carefully.

08:16.560 --> 08:17.750
When you've made your decision,

08:17.750 --> 08:18.810
come meet me again.

08:19.240 --> 08:19.920
However,

08:20.720 --> 08:22.250
you need to decide quickly.

08:22.720 --> 08:24.320
My execution is coming soon.

08:24.870 --> 08:26.470
I can't wait too long for you.

08:37.840 --> 08:38.640
Immortal Xin,

08:39.200 --> 08:40.440
I'm being honest with you.

08:40.440 --> 08:41.840
Throughout this prison,

08:42.000 --> 08:43.150
in terms of knowledge and looks,

08:43.150 --> 08:44.240
no one suits you

08:44.270 --> 08:45.480
better than Lord Lu.

08:45.580 --> 08:47.440
And no one's execution date
is closer than his.

08:47.440 --> 08:48.170
To be honest,

08:48.480 --> 08:50.010
it's happening this month.

08:50.390 --> 08:51.790
What crime did he commit?

08:52.240 --> 08:53.840
Why is he sentenced to death?

08:55.000 --> 08:55.870
Well...

08:56.960 --> 08:58.020
In my point of view,

08:58.270 --> 08:59.800
even if you two get married,

08:59.960 --> 09:01.440
you won't have many days together.

09:01.440 --> 09:03.240
There's really no need to know too much,

09:03.240 --> 09:04.840
just to avoid unnecessary distress.

09:04.840 --> 09:06.240
Isn't this what you wanted?

09:06.240 --> 09:07.440
A death row prisoner,

09:07.440 --> 09:08.550
guilty of heinous crimes,

09:08.550 --> 09:09.790
with only days left to live.

09:09.790 --> 09:11.990
Doesn't he meet all your requirements?

09:14.030 --> 09:15.230
Now that you're back,

09:15.440 --> 09:17.100
do you have a place to lodge in?

09:17.600 --> 09:18.670
I'm going to my aunt's house.

09:18.670 --> 09:19.320
She lives

09:19.320 --> 09:20.920
nearby in the Tianshui Lane.

09:21.550 --> 09:22.950
It's good to have family.

09:23.840 --> 09:24.960
Before I entered the immortal sect,

09:24.960 --> 09:25.910
my aunt was the one

09:25.910 --> 09:27.150
closest to me in my family.

09:27.150 --> 09:29.000
Since I can stick around longer this time,

09:29.000 --> 09:30.360
it's perfect to stay by her side

09:30.360 --> 09:31.360
and attend to her.

09:34.910 --> 09:39.230
[Xin's Mansion, Wei County]

09:53.720 --> 09:54.720
My Lady,

09:55.550 --> 09:56.720
you're back.

10:03.480 --> 10:04.390
Xin Mei.

10:05.270 --> 10:06.270
A cultivator.

10:16.900 --> 10:19.340
[The memorial tablet
of late Mrs. Xin, who was born a Chen]

10:25.600 --> 10:26.390
Auntie.

10:29.450 --> 10:30.380
I'm Xin Mei.

10:33.150 --> 10:34.100
I'm back.

10:42.510 --> 10:43.030
Liu,

10:43.320 --> 10:44.620
how's that one's case going?

10:44.620 --> 10:45.240
There's no hope?

10:45.240 --> 10:46.570
Just look at what he did.

10:46.750 --> 10:47.960
Who would dare save him?

10:47.960 --> 10:49.890
Is there anyone left in his family?

10:50.720 --> 10:52.720
They say his parents died long ago.

10:53.120 --> 10:54.580
He has no siblings either.

10:54.670 --> 10:56.470
He's never even gotten married.

10:56.750 --> 10:57.790
His life has been

10:58.320 --> 10:59.390
truly miserable.

10:59.750 --> 11:00.790
But that doesn't mean he can

11:00.790 --> 11:02.050
get married in prison.

11:02.720 --> 11:04.380
He must've used enough money.

11:06.200 --> 11:07.840
Chief Chu arranged it.

11:08.890 --> 11:09.670
Never mind.

11:09.870 --> 11:10.960
Come on, Liu, let's drink.

11:10.960 --> 11:11.420
Cheers.

11:22.120 --> 11:23.580
That bird flew back again.

11:23.600 --> 11:24.930
It's been watching you.

11:27.870 --> 11:28.510
Hurry.

11:31.630 --> 11:32.910
Just routine.

11:33.760 --> 11:34.820
Her surname is Xin.

11:35.400 --> 11:37.320
Xin Xiong, the master of Xin Xie Manor,

11:37.320 --> 11:38.520
has the same surname.

11:39.750 --> 11:40.550
That's right.

11:40.870 --> 11:42.670
But they're not blood-related.

11:42.750 --> 11:43.870
She has great talent

11:43.870 --> 11:45.000
as a born cultivator,

11:45.000 --> 11:46.270
a once-in-ten-thousand kind

11:46.270 --> 11:47.390
of cultivation prodigy.

11:47.390 --> 11:49.390
Years ago,
when Xin Xiong traveled down the mountain

11:49.390 --> 11:50.360
and passed through Wei County,

11:50.360 --> 11:51.360
he came across her

11:51.440 --> 11:53.240
and took her in as his disciple.

11:54.750 --> 11:55.870
A born cultivator.

11:56.840 --> 11:57.640
How old is she?

11:58.510 --> 11:59.970
I don't know her exact age.

12:00.360 --> 12:00.890
However,

12:00.960 --> 12:03.270
her parents and relatives
have all died of old age.

12:03.270 --> 12:04.270
Only one remains.

12:04.270 --> 12:06.000
That is her aunt, who's over 90.

12:06.120 --> 12:07.450
So she must not be young.

12:08.240 --> 12:09.270
If she's that old

12:09.870 --> 12:11.270
and is a born cultivator,

12:11.360 --> 12:12.080
why is she only

12:12.080 --> 12:13.680
in the Qi Cultivation Realm?

12:14.600 --> 12:15.730
I find it weird, too.

12:15.960 --> 12:16.560
By the way,

12:16.960 --> 12:18.960
she was also born on September 9.

12:19.320 --> 12:20.200
September 9?

12:21.150 --> 12:23.240
Back then, the Mad Daoist foresaw
the heavenly secrets

12:23.240 --> 12:24.550
and made two prophecies.

12:24.550 --> 12:25.240
First,

12:25.270 --> 12:27.390
the world would face
a catastrophic disaster.

12:27.390 --> 12:28.120
Second,

12:28.320 --> 12:29.850
someone born on September 9

12:30.150 --> 12:31.870
would be the savior of the world.

12:31.870 --> 12:32.720
Since then,

12:32.960 --> 12:34.240
all major sects began enrolling

12:34.240 --> 12:36.150
disciples born on that date.

12:36.480 --> 12:38.000
They call them "Heavenly Talents."

12:38.000 --> 12:38.550
Xin Mei is

12:38.670 --> 12:40.730
the Heavenly Talent of Xin Xie Manor.

12:42.670 --> 12:43.640
She doesn't look

12:43.960 --> 12:45.620
like a Heavenly Talent at all.

12:46.790 --> 12:48.720
Many people are born on the same day.

12:48.720 --> 12:50.630
Could they all be saviors of the world?

12:50.630 --> 12:51.390
Anyway,

12:51.630 --> 12:53.750
she wants to find a poor thing to marry.

12:53.750 --> 12:55.600
And you want to find

12:55.790 --> 12:56.670
a cultivator as your wife.

12:56.670 --> 12:58.400
Aren't you two a perfect match?

12:59.600 --> 13:00.800
Just wait patiently.

13:01.080 --> 13:02.120
Before the execution,

13:02.120 --> 13:02.790
you two must

13:02.790 --> 13:03.670
get this done.

13:07.080 --> 13:07.930
Your auntie

13:08.440 --> 13:10.150
lived a long life.

13:10.960 --> 13:13.080
She passed away peacefully in her sleep.

13:13.080 --> 13:13.630
At least

13:13.870 --> 13:14.670
she didn't suffer.

13:14.670 --> 13:15.320
Chubby.

13:16.840 --> 13:18.270
You've changed so much.

13:18.930 --> 13:21.200
[Sun Yao (Chubby)]

13:19.000 --> 13:19.750
I'm old now.

13:20.280 --> 13:21.540
How could I not change?

13:21.910 --> 13:23.550
You're still amazing, though.

13:23.550 --> 13:25.210
You look just a few years older

13:25.270 --> 13:26.330
than when you left.

13:26.750 --> 13:28.550
Being an immortal has its perks.

13:30.270 --> 13:31.930
It's not as great as you think.

13:32.270 --> 13:33.130
What about you?

13:33.200 --> 13:35.080
How have you been all these years?

13:35.600 --> 13:36.480
Getting by.

13:36.870 --> 13:37.670
How about you?

13:38.120 --> 13:39.870
What are you usually busy with?

13:41.030 --> 13:43.080
Mostly meditation and cultivation.

13:43.080 --> 13:44.220
Sometimes I help my master

13:44.220 --> 13:45.390
with small affairs.

13:45.750 --> 13:47.210
Nothing special, really.

13:47.790 --> 13:48.920
Like slaying demons

13:49.030 --> 13:50.030
or saving people?

13:50.130 --> 13:51.460
It's not that dramatic.

13:52.840 --> 13:53.720
In a few days,

13:53.960 --> 13:56.240
let's invite our old neighborhood friends

13:56.240 --> 13:57.370
for a get-together.

13:57.510 --> 13:59.170
Everyone's been missing you.

13:59.270 --> 14:00.000
Sounds good.

14:00.390 --> 14:01.870
I haven't seen them for ages.

14:01.870 --> 14:02.630
Right?

14:03.600 --> 14:04.390
Well,

14:05.030 --> 14:06.830
now that my aunt has passed away,

14:07.440 --> 14:09.910
the only blood relative
I have left in this world

14:09.910 --> 14:10.640
is gone, too.

14:10.820 --> 14:11.980
Don't be silly.

14:12.480 --> 14:13.960
Your aunt wasn't even

14:13.960 --> 14:15.290
related to you by blood.

14:15.550 --> 14:17.030
Your uncle died long ago.

14:17.320 --> 14:18.320
In this world,

14:18.480 --> 14:20.680
you've long lost your blood relatives.

14:34.070 --> 14:35.690
[Song's Pastries]

14:36.200 --> 14:36.840
Oh, right.

14:37.510 --> 14:40.170
I promised to bring him
some pastries last time.

14:42.870 --> 14:43.730
It's this room.

14:43.750 --> 14:45.350
Call me if you need anything.

14:50.270 --> 14:51.270
When Mei arrives,

14:51.600 --> 14:52.930
let's ask her properly.

14:53.080 --> 14:54.340
I think you're just...

15:01.200 --> 15:01.750
Mei,

15:02.000 --> 15:02.790
welcome.

15:02.890 --> 15:04.020
Come on, take a seat.

15:04.360 --> 15:05.120
This is Mei?

15:05.440 --> 15:05.750
Yes.

15:05.750 --> 15:06.550
This is Mei.

15:06.550 --> 15:07.360
It seems so.

15:07.720 --> 15:09.150
-So young.
-She looks so young.

15:09.150 --> 15:10.080
Indeed.

15:10.150 --> 15:10.870
This is Mei.

15:10.870 --> 15:11.750
This is really her.

15:11.750 --> 15:12.210
Well...

15:12.270 --> 15:13.330
This is really Mei.

15:14.060 --> 15:15.300
You really are Mei?

15:16.030 --> 15:17.480
You look so young,

15:17.840 --> 15:19.640
not at all like someone your age.

15:19.720 --> 15:20.100
Exactly.

15:20.100 --> 15:20.630
Mei,

15:21.360 --> 15:22.510
you've truly become an immortal?

15:22.510 --> 15:23.320
Mei,

15:23.840 --> 15:26.600
I heard that immortals can fly
and move through the earth

15:26.600 --> 15:27.600
and never age.

15:28.120 --> 15:29.910
Are you also immortal?

15:30.270 --> 15:32.600
No, no. It's way too exaggerated.

15:33.320 --> 15:34.390
People say

15:35.040 --> 15:36.480
the heavenly ladder is broken.

15:36.480 --> 15:38.550
Cultivators can't ascend to heaven

15:38.750 --> 15:40.280
or become deities anymore.

15:40.670 --> 15:42.670
Apart from knowing some magic spells,

15:42.670 --> 15:43.930
they just live longer.

15:45.200 --> 15:46.360
That's all.

15:46.670 --> 15:47.270
Mei,

15:47.960 --> 15:48.720
you need to

15:48.750 --> 15:49.810
show us something.

15:50.050 --> 15:51.290
Yes, show us.

15:51.320 --> 15:52.030
Show us.

15:52.050 --> 15:52.720
Come on.

15:52.840 --> 15:54.600
Well, alright then.

16:04.270 --> 16:04.670
That

16:04.960 --> 16:05.550
is all?

16:05.550 --> 16:06.350
Well, this...

16:07.200 --> 16:09.320
This is turning water into ice?

16:11.200 --> 16:13.080
I had an incident years ago.

16:13.510 --> 16:15.040
My cultivation went wrong.

16:15.390 --> 16:16.920
So my level isn't that high.

16:17.200 --> 16:18.630
Not that high?

16:18.870 --> 16:19.930
Then how high is it?

16:20.030 --> 16:21.690
A cultivator of Nascent Soul?

16:23.510 --> 16:24.630
Or of Golden Core?

16:25.840 --> 16:27.700
I'm at mid-level Qi Cultivation.

16:27.870 --> 16:29.130
Qi Cultivation Realm?

16:30.020 --> 16:32.300
Isn't that the lowest level?

16:32.920 --> 16:33.590
Yes.

16:34.200 --> 16:35.600
Still better than you!

16:36.200 --> 16:36.720
Mei,

16:37.550 --> 16:39.790
if you're not usually busy,

16:40.380 --> 16:41.600
why didn't you come back

16:41.600 --> 16:42.860
to visit us more often?

16:43.510 --> 16:44.550
You have no idea.

16:45.030 --> 16:46.360
People from immortal sects

16:46.360 --> 16:48.400
cannot interfere in mortal affairs.

16:48.400 --> 16:50.820
This is the rule set
by the Twelve Immortal Sects

16:50.820 --> 16:52.150
and the imperial court.

16:52.910 --> 16:54.310
Every disciple who joins

16:54.670 --> 16:56.720
must take a Soul Oath,

16:57.120 --> 16:59.000
so of course she can't return at will.

16:59.000 --> 16:59.550
Mei,

16:59.840 --> 17:00.840
am I right?

17:01.790 --> 17:02.720
That's correct.

17:03.150 --> 17:04.280
You know quite a lot.

17:05.270 --> 17:06.310
Do you know

17:06.310 --> 17:07.510
an official named Lu?

17:08.240 --> 17:08.750
Who?

17:08.920 --> 17:11.310
Lu Huai,
with "Huai" from "Wood" and "Ghost."

17:11.310 --> 17:13.010
He was once a county official here.

17:13.010 --> 17:14.079
Why mention him?

17:14.109 --> 17:15.230
Why bring up someone like him?

17:15.230 --> 17:16.440
What for?

17:16.790 --> 17:17.440
He deserves to die.

17:17.440 --> 17:18.109
Mei.

17:19.829 --> 17:20.880
Do you know him?

17:21.349 --> 17:22.200
Sort of.

17:24.270 --> 17:25.829
It's a long story.

17:26.310 --> 17:27.310
Six months ago,

17:27.960 --> 17:29.880
the Yong region suffered a great flood.

17:29.880 --> 17:31.540
Dikes broke, fields flooded,

17:32.070 --> 17:33.830
people became homeless.

17:34.400 --> 17:36.690
Our Wei County was relatively fortunate.

17:36.690 --> 17:38.170
In the worst-hit cities,

17:38.200 --> 17:39.350
it's said

17:39.750 --> 17:42.110
that corpses piled up like mountains,

17:42.350 --> 17:43.880
tragedies filled the city,

17:44.270 --> 17:46.550
and barely one in ten households survived.

17:46.550 --> 17:48.480
People were filthy and ghostlike.

17:48.480 --> 17:50.110
They had nothing to eat.

17:50.440 --> 17:53.000
People even ate weeds, clay, and tree bark

17:53.110 --> 17:54.440
to fill their stomachs.

17:54.880 --> 17:57.350
It truly is hell on earth.

17:57.830 --> 18:00.110
Later, the imperial court issued an order,

18:00.110 --> 18:01.550
commanding the surrounding prefectures

18:01.550 --> 18:03.310
to send grain to the Yong region.

18:03.310 --> 18:04.720
They also issued a strict decree

18:04.720 --> 18:06.750
to forbid grain merchants
from raising prices

18:06.750 --> 18:08.950
and urge them to sell
at 50% of the normal price

18:08.950 --> 18:10.350
to the disaster victims.

18:10.790 --> 18:13.030
All regions followed
the imperial court's decree

18:13.030 --> 18:14.390
to provide disaster relief.

18:14.390 --> 18:15.820
But only Lu Huai was

18:14.650 --> 18:16.790
[Wei County Government]

18:16.130 --> 18:17.850
bold as brass

18:18.030 --> 18:19.720
and did exactly the opposite.

18:19.960 --> 18:21.440
Not only did he disregard
the imperial edict,

18:21.440 --> 18:23.480
but he also accepted bribes
from grain merchants,

18:23.480 --> 18:24.830
allowing them to sell grain

18:24.830 --> 18:26.200
at inflated prices in Wei County.

18:26.200 --> 18:27.070
As a result,

18:27.200 --> 18:30.070
grain prices in Wei County
remained exorbitantly high.

18:30.070 --> 18:32.390
The prefects jointly submitted a memorial,

18:32.390 --> 18:33.790
sentencing that corrupt official

18:33.790 --> 18:34.960
to dismissal from office

18:34.960 --> 18:36.820
and exile three thousand li away.

18:37.240 --> 18:38.830
But he showed no remorse

18:39.070 --> 18:41.030
and talked nonsense recklessly in court,

18:41.030 --> 18:41.920
making wild accusations,

18:41.920 --> 18:43.510
attempting to escape punishment

18:43.510 --> 18:45.370
by dragging others down with him.

18:45.450 --> 18:47.680
This infuriated Minister Liang Wenjing
of the Court of Judicial Review so much

18:47.680 --> 18:48.290
that Lord Liang

18:48.290 --> 18:49.640
personally took over the trial

18:49.640 --> 18:52.170
and sentenced him
to death by a thousand cuts.

18:53.920 --> 18:54.550
Qiu,

18:54.790 --> 18:55.680
when Lord Liang was

18:55.680 --> 18:56.920
trying Lu Huai that day,

18:56.920 --> 18:58.480
weren't you there watching, too?

18:58.480 --> 19:00.010
Did you hear what they said?

19:01.060 --> 19:02.550
He was like a rat caught in a trap

19:02.550 --> 19:04.080
with no power to fight back,

19:04.550 --> 19:05.950
who could only yap madly.

19:06.110 --> 19:07.240
Nothing special.

19:07.960 --> 19:08.680
Is he

19:09.440 --> 19:10.790
really that kind of person?

19:10.790 --> 19:11.440
Mei,

19:12.640 --> 19:14.170
how did you come to know him?

19:14.720 --> 19:15.200
I...

19:16.230 --> 19:17.720
No matter how you knew him,

19:18.110 --> 19:18.790
just don't

19:19.200 --> 19:20.750
get involved in his affairs.

19:20.750 --> 19:22.920
For one thing, he's a corrupt official.

19:22.920 --> 19:23.680
In Wei County,

19:23.680 --> 19:25.750
everyone would gladly tear him apart

19:25.770 --> 19:26.770
or skin him alive.

19:26.960 --> 19:27.360
Right.

19:27.880 --> 19:29.810
For another, you're a cultivator,

19:30.090 --> 19:30.920
and cultivators

19:30.920 --> 19:32.880
shouldn't interfere in mortal affairs.

19:32.880 --> 19:35.810
Reckless interference
will ruin your cultivation.

19:36.240 --> 19:36.960
Well said.

19:37.070 --> 19:37.960
Right, let's drink. Cheers.

19:37.960 --> 19:38.400
Come on.

19:38.400 --> 19:38.750
Cheers.

19:38.750 --> 19:39.680
Come on.

19:39.830 --> 19:40.290
Cheers.

19:57.720 --> 20:00.180
I've thought it over.
You're very suitable.

20:00.720 --> 20:01.790
I was born in Wei County.

20:01.790 --> 20:02.790
In my youth, guided by my master,

20:02.790 --> 20:04.510
I entered an immortal sect
for cultivation.

20:04.510 --> 20:05.970
It's been sixty years now.

20:06.000 --> 20:07.110
My cultivation is ordinary,

20:07.110 --> 20:08.970
and my family has all passed away.

20:09.640 --> 20:10.590
If we marry,

20:10.960 --> 20:12.590
I will burn offerings for you.

20:12.590 --> 20:14.880
Not just during Qingming Festival
and holidays,

20:14.880 --> 20:16.600
but also on your birthday
and death anniversary.

20:16.600 --> 20:17.680
I won't let you suffer from poverty

20:17.680 --> 20:18.740
in the underworld.

20:19.030 --> 20:19.550
Also,

20:20.000 --> 20:21.790
if I get married and have children,

20:21.790 --> 20:22.590
I will have them

20:22.590 --> 20:24.720
worship and pay tribute to you as well.

20:24.790 --> 20:25.880
That's my case.

20:26.400 --> 20:28.130
Do you have any other requests?

20:31.310 --> 20:32.440
Why are you smiling?

20:32.790 --> 20:33.510
Nothing.

20:36.680 --> 20:38.070
Well then, how do you like

20:38.070 --> 20:39.130
the wedding items?

20:40.680 --> 20:41.440
You agreed?

20:41.790 --> 20:42.440
I did.

20:44.310 --> 20:45.170
As for the items

20:45.590 --> 20:47.590
like the wedding clothes,
headpieces, and candles,

20:47.590 --> 20:48.850
I'll prepare them all.

20:49.200 --> 20:51.000
I'll register at the government office.

20:51.000 --> 20:52.460
Once everything is ready,

20:52.480 --> 20:53.810
we can hold the wedding.

20:55.110 --> 20:55.480
Good.

20:56.640 --> 20:58.000
Although you can't leave,

20:58.000 --> 20:59.930
I've asked Constable Chu about it.

21:00.280 --> 21:01.200
The wedding ceremony

21:01.200 --> 21:02.460
can be held right here.

21:03.680 --> 21:04.940
Do you have any family?

21:05.030 --> 21:06.490
I can invite them all over.

21:06.640 --> 21:07.570
I have no family.

21:08.350 --> 21:09.350
What about friends?

21:09.350 --> 21:10.080
None either.

21:11.270 --> 21:11.880
Me, too.

21:12.510 --> 21:13.910
So it's just the two of us.

21:14.350 --> 21:15.680
The two of us are enough.

21:18.910 --> 21:19.890
Didn't you say last time

21:19.890 --> 21:21.440
that when you came to see me again,

21:21.440 --> 21:22.960
you would bring me some snacks?

21:22.960 --> 21:23.820
Where are they?

21:24.110 --> 21:24.910
Immortal Xin,

21:24.950 --> 21:26.110
are these your pastries?

21:26.110 --> 21:27.370
I saw you bring them in.

21:29.460 --> 21:30.350
I don't want them.

21:30.350 --> 21:31.280
They're for you.

21:36.920 --> 21:37.510
I forgot.

21:39.200 --> 21:40.330
You're a cultivator

21:40.590 --> 21:41.920
with such a poor memory?

21:48.350 --> 21:49.150
Just a minute.

22:03.550 --> 22:04.410
This is for you.

22:06.880 --> 22:08.930
Thank you for your hard work these days.

22:08.930 --> 22:09.750
I'm imprisoned

22:09.750 --> 22:10.880
and can't help much.

22:11.070 --> 22:11.790
This money

22:12.120 --> 22:13.000
should be enough

22:13.000 --> 22:14.600
to buy all the wedding items.

22:15.480 --> 22:16.590
You can spend extra

22:16.880 --> 22:19.010
to have merchants prepare in advance.

22:19.240 --> 22:20.970
Although my sentence is fixed,

22:21.130 --> 22:22.440
if there are any changes,

22:22.440 --> 22:23.770
and it's moved up by a few days,

22:23.770 --> 22:24.630
we won't have to

22:24.640 --> 22:25.570
rush it in panic.

22:32.200 --> 22:32.930
What's this?

22:34.270 --> 22:34.830
A gift.

22:35.640 --> 22:36.440
For me?

22:37.350 --> 22:38.680
It's nothing valuable,

22:39.160 --> 22:40.550
just blessed at the temple

22:40.550 --> 22:41.480
for protection.

22:45.030 --> 22:45.890
What about you?

22:46.160 --> 22:47.690
Do you have anything for me?

22:49.400 --> 22:50.000
No.

22:53.830 --> 22:54.590
What's that?

22:56.200 --> 22:57.000
Not this one.

22:57.720 --> 22:58.980
It's for someone else.

23:03.030 --> 23:03.630
All right.

23:07.750 --> 23:08.590
Xin Mei,

23:09.550 --> 23:10.160
thank you

23:10.680 --> 23:12.080
for agreeing to marry me.

23:30.930 --> 23:36.650
[Blessing Candle]

23:33.570 --> 23:34.160
Sir,

23:34.720 --> 23:36.720
just prepare according to the list.

23:42.880 --> 23:44.000
Xin Mei, Xin Mei.

23:44.270 --> 23:45.600
Have you seen your aunt?

23:45.880 --> 23:47.070
Have you wrapped things up?

23:47.070 --> 23:48.840
You've repeatedly broken
the rules of the immortal sects.

23:48.840 --> 23:50.480
Your cultivation has dropped
three times already.

23:50.480 --> 23:51.750
Do not meddle in others' affairs again.

23:51.750 --> 23:52.810
Come back quickly.

23:54.160 --> 23:55.680
This troublesome disciple
only listens to you.

23:55.680 --> 23:57.350
If you still don't return
to Xin Xie Manor,

23:57.350 --> 23:59.420
I truly cannot bear
to stay here another day.

23:59.420 --> 24:00.940
Xin Mei, Xin Mei.

24:01.400 --> 24:02.590
Have you seen your aunt?

24:02.590 --> 24:04.120
Have you wrapped things up?

24:04.200 --> 24:05.320
Tell Master

24:05.970 --> 24:07.110
that I still have some matters

24:07.110 --> 24:07.810
to attend to.

24:07.810 --> 24:10.110
I'll need some more time
before I can return.

24:10.110 --> 24:10.640
Also,

24:11.030 --> 24:12.790
Sheng is a well-behaved, good girl.

24:12.790 --> 24:13.700
If you don't provoke her,

24:13.700 --> 24:15.430
she won't give you any trouble.

24:15.480 --> 24:16.960
You two should get along well at home

24:16.960 --> 24:17.820
until I return.

24:17.920 --> 24:18.850
Repeat after me.

24:18.970 --> 24:20.110
I still have some matters

24:20.110 --> 24:20.890
to attend to.

24:20.920 --> 24:22.720
I'll need some more time
before I can return.

24:22.720 --> 24:24.750
Also, Sheng is a well-behaved, good girl.

24:24.750 --> 24:25.750
If you don't provoke her,

24:25.750 --> 24:27.170
she won't cause you any trouble.

24:27.170 --> 24:28.830
You two should get along well at home

24:28.830 --> 24:29.690
until I return.

24:30.270 --> 24:30.870
Off you go.

24:41.450 --> 24:42.070
Liu.

24:42.560 --> 24:43.310
What are you sniffing

24:43.310 --> 24:44.310
so passionately?

24:44.680 --> 24:46.200
This is the handkerchief

24:46.270 --> 24:47.310
left by that immortal lady
who came last time.

24:47.310 --> 24:48.480
You're such a creep.

24:49.720 --> 24:50.650
What do you know?

24:51.260 --> 24:52.160
The scent of this immortal lady

24:52.160 --> 24:53.920
fills my heart with content.

25:00.480 --> 25:01.480
You know nothing.

25:09.680 --> 25:10.270
Liu!

25:10.640 --> 25:11.900
What's wrong with you?

25:12.350 --> 25:12.790
Liu!

25:13.480 --> 25:14.030
Liu!

25:14.480 --> 25:15.350
Get up, please!

25:17.110 --> 25:17.750
Liu!

25:30.480 --> 25:31.000
Lu.

25:32.240 --> 25:33.840
What did Liu do to offend you?

25:34.000 --> 25:35.350
You almost killed him.

25:37.960 --> 25:38.400
Couldn't you

25:38.400 --> 25:39.880
wait until nighttime to do it?

25:39.880 --> 25:41.480
In broad daylight like this,

25:41.510 --> 25:44.440
even blaming it on ghosts
wouldn't convince anyone.

25:44.780 --> 25:45.490
Also,

25:46.120 --> 25:48.000
for that green lotus jade pendant,

25:48.000 --> 25:49.530
you just gave it away to her?

25:49.680 --> 25:51.680
That was a high-class magical talisman.

25:51.680 --> 25:53.140
Don't you feel any regret?

25:54.550 --> 25:55.610
She's marrying me.

25:56.270 --> 25:58.270
She's the one making the sacrifice.

25:58.350 --> 25:59.880
It's just my compensation.

26:01.270 --> 26:02.400
How generous of you.

26:16.480 --> 26:17.270
Auntie.

26:18.310 --> 26:19.510
Please rest in peace.

26:20.070 --> 26:21.030
People

26:21.270 --> 26:23.130
become useless when they get old.

26:23.350 --> 26:25.110
Cultivating immortality is much better.

26:25.110 --> 26:26.270
It gives you a long life

26:26.270 --> 26:27.680
and a robust body.

26:28.560 --> 26:29.140
If there were

26:29.140 --> 26:30.870
a chance to do it all over again,

26:31.000 --> 26:33.200
would you choose to leave home
to cultivate immortality?

26:33.200 --> 26:34.200
Of course.

26:34.200 --> 26:36.200
Who wouldn't want to be an immortal?

26:40.000 --> 26:41.030
Not necessarily.

26:41.960 --> 26:43.760
Everyone has their own destiny,

26:44.000 --> 26:46.640
yet we should learn to be happy
with what we have.

26:46.640 --> 26:48.720
Ordinary people seek fulfillment in life;

26:48.720 --> 26:51.110
immortals seek fulfillment
in their cultivation.

26:51.110 --> 26:51.910
But in the end,

26:52.160 --> 26:54.090
what truly counts as fulfillment?

26:54.680 --> 26:56.480
I've entered the immortal sect,

26:56.480 --> 26:57.030
but

26:57.640 --> 26:59.500
because my mind isn't steadfast,

26:59.510 --> 27:01.790
I can't make any breakthroughs
in cultivation.

27:01.790 --> 27:02.960
My family raised me,

27:03.550 --> 27:05.590
yet I couldn't take good care of them.

27:05.590 --> 27:06.790
I couldn't even

27:07.240 --> 27:09.370
be by their side in their last moments.

27:10.440 --> 27:11.770
So they should blame me,

27:12.680 --> 27:13.740
and rightfully so.

27:14.480 --> 27:16.340
The strongest bonds in this world

27:16.830 --> 27:18.490
are those of blood and family.

27:19.160 --> 27:20.440
You're family.

27:20.790 --> 27:21.960
How could they bear

27:22.110 --> 27:23.350
to blame you?

27:24.160 --> 27:25.690
Do you see that plot of land?

27:26.790 --> 27:27.790
That's the burial site

27:27.790 --> 27:29.790
your grandfather reserved for you.

27:29.960 --> 27:31.920
Before he passed away,

27:32.310 --> 27:34.720
you were his greatest concern.

27:35.350 --> 27:37.880
He feared that when you returned
from your cultivation,

27:37.880 --> 27:39.610
you couldn't find your family.

27:39.880 --> 27:42.540
So he specifically kept
this burial plot for you

27:42.720 --> 27:45.640
to return to your "home."

27:45.150 --> 27:48.640
[Here rests the late Mrs. Xin, Chen Yunci]

27:50.880 --> 27:52.400
My Lady, welcome back.

27:52.790 --> 27:54.270
Just now, several shops

27:54.270 --> 27:55.510
delivered items for you.

27:55.510 --> 27:57.070
They said you ordered them.

27:57.200 --> 27:58.790
They looked quite valuable,

27:58.790 --> 28:00.450
so I put them in the inner room.

28:01.240 --> 28:01.880
Thank you.

28:38.270 --> 28:38.830
Mr. Lu,

28:39.480 --> 28:41.640
here are the wedding clothes
sent by Immortal Xin.

28:41.640 --> 28:42.840
They look so festive.

28:44.550 --> 28:45.750
I'll leave them here.

28:46.070 --> 28:48.330
It's a pity that you can't see the colors.

29:25.050 --> 29:25.850
Bride,

29:26.400 --> 29:27.870
the sedan chair has arrived

29:27.870 --> 29:29.030
and is waiting outside.

29:29.030 --> 29:30.030
You can get in now.

29:30.270 --> 29:31.200
I'm coming.

29:54.390 --> 29:58.320
♪ Honor and disgrace;
rumors and prejudice ♪

29:59.110 --> 30:02.510
♪ Everyone has their own take ♪

30:03.150 --> 30:06.970
♪ Fingers coated in blood
and disasters brought about ♪

30:07.000 --> 30:10.230
♪ Were never what I wanted ♪

30:10.530 --> 30:14.370
♪ The great way is fading away,
besieged by mysterious traps ♪

30:15.230 --> 30:18.980
♪ Who dares to treat life and death
as nothing? ♪

30:19.010 --> 30:22.730
♪ In the blink of an eye, the body
collapses, and the soul is destroyed ♪

30:22.750 --> 30:27.730
♪ The fire starts raging across the land ♪

30:28.500 --> 30:30.550
♪ What do you think is ♪

30:30.570 --> 30:32.850
♪ The most impressive farewell
in the world? ♪

30:33.220 --> 30:36.350
♪ The endless slaughter and massacres ♪

30:37.190 --> 30:41.140
♪ Do not wait until that thin snow
on the eaves ♪

30:41.170 --> 30:44.390
♪ Turns a young man's hair white
before you regret it ♪

30:44.950 --> 30:46.690
♪ When you think ♪

30:46.710 --> 30:49.140
♪ The bloody strife
would come to an end? ♪

30:49.170 --> 30:52.490
♪ Burn myself to prove it
without looking back ♪

30:53.040 --> 30:57.010
♪ Holding the morning glow in hand,
I paint the world ♪

30:57.050 --> 31:03.230
♪ The dawn light
illuminates the vast sky ♪

31:13.200 --> 31:13.730
Alright,

31:14.310 --> 31:15.310
you may stop here.

31:16.510 --> 31:20.510
♪ Honor and disgrace;
rumors and prejudice ♪

31:16.790 --> 31:17.440
Bride,

31:17.920 --> 31:19.120
I'll see you off here.

31:19.640 --> 31:21.240
May your life ahead

31:21.270 --> 31:24.260
♪ Everyone has their own take ♪

31:21.680 --> 31:24.080
be filled with happiness and good fortune.

31:24.790 --> 31:25.480
Thank you.

31:25.170 --> 31:28.820
♪ Fingers coated in blood
and disasters brought about ♪

31:29.040 --> 31:32.220
♪ Were never what I wanted ♪

31:32.550 --> 31:36.280
♪ The great way is fading away,
besieged by mysterious traps ♪

31:36.880 --> 31:37.510
Take it slow.

31:37.170 --> 31:40.960
♪ Who dares to treat life and death
as nothing? ♪

31:38.310 --> 31:39.030
Follow me.

31:40.980 --> 31:44.910
♪ In the blink of an eye, the body
collapses, and the soul is destroyed ♪

31:44.930 --> 31:48.390
♪ The fire starts raging across the land ♪

31:48.520 --> 31:50.530
♪ What do you think is ♪

31:50.560 --> 31:52.890
♪ The most impressive farewell
in the world? ♪

31:53.170 --> 31:56.480
♪ The endless slaughter and massacres ♪

31:57.210 --> 32:01.080
♪ Do not wait until that thin snow
on the eaves ♪

32:01.480 --> 32:04.450
♪ Turns a young man's hair white
before you regret it ♪

32:04.960 --> 32:06.540
♪ When you think ♪

32:06.570 --> 32:09.000
♪ The bloody strife
would come to an end? ♪

32:09.270 --> 32:12.250
♪ End these everlasting battles ♪

32:13.120 --> 32:17.060
♪ Holding the morning glow in hand,
I paint the world ♪

32:17.190 --> 32:21.470
♪ Someone's got to clean up this mess ♪

32:27.000 --> 32:29.200
A strand of your black hair is entwined,

32:29.310 --> 32:31.310
bound together for life.

32:47.030 --> 32:48.290
This wedding ceremony

32:48.310 --> 32:50.350
should have parents and family present,

32:50.350 --> 32:52.240
with friends and relatives in attendance.

32:52.240 --> 32:53.040
But you two are

32:53.270 --> 32:54.670
both alone in this world,

32:55.320 --> 32:57.560
with neither parents nor relatives.

32:57.920 --> 32:58.640
Therefore,

32:59.310 --> 33:01.570
you can only bow to the matchmaker deity.

33:07.310 --> 33:08.400
It's the auspicious time.

33:08.400 --> 33:10.130
A promise to grow old together,

33:10.510 --> 33:12.510
with a good marriage forever bound.

33:12.680 --> 33:14.070
A complementary pair,

33:14.920 --> 33:16.550
a perfect match.

33:19.720 --> 33:21.380
First bow to heaven and earth.

33:33.480 --> 33:35.110
Second bow to the parents.

33:42.830 --> 33:44.490
The couple bows to each other.

34:05.720 --> 34:06.270
Xin Mei,

34:07.480 --> 34:08.080
thank you.

34:09.230 --> 34:10.760
I should also say thank you.

36:02.430 --> 36:03.310
[Lu's Mansion]

36:03.340 --> 36:04.970
[You deserve a terrible death!]

36:04.990 --> 36:07.060
[Treacherous, corrupt official]

36:14.320 --> 36:15.180
I need to go now.

36:17.670 --> 36:18.760
Going back to your sect?

36:18.760 --> 36:20.090
I'm leaving Wei County.

36:20.880 --> 36:21.940
I came down from the mountain this time

36:21.940 --> 36:23.870
to handle some important matters.

36:24.230 --> 36:26.000
Now that my personal affairs are settled,

36:26.000 --> 36:27.200
I should set off soon.

36:29.150 --> 36:30.610
Take care on your journey.

36:33.760 --> 36:35.420
How much time do you have left?

36:36.360 --> 36:37.030
Not long.

36:37.630 --> 36:38.670
Just a few days.

36:40.590 --> 36:41.650
Aren't you scared?

36:42.960 --> 36:43.760
Of course I am.

36:44.210 --> 36:45.980
It's death by 1,000 cuts.

36:46.510 --> 36:47.800
How could I not be afraid?

36:47.800 --> 36:49.400
But what's the point of fear?

36:49.920 --> 36:51.320
On this joyous day of mine,

36:51.320 --> 36:52.650
I can't just cry, right?

36:53.670 --> 36:54.870
Do you regret it then?

36:55.880 --> 36:56.360
What?

36:57.670 --> 36:59.000
The things you've done,

36:59.630 --> 37:02.160
like taking bribes,
inflating grain prices,

37:02.710 --> 37:04.970
defying orders, and harming the people.

37:05.510 --> 37:06.240
Do you regret

37:07.070 --> 37:08.070
what you've done?

37:09.000 --> 37:10.600
You've been asking about me.

37:13.930 --> 37:14.840
Everyone should take

37:14.840 --> 37:16.590
responsibility for their actions.

37:16.590 --> 37:17.190
Perhaps

37:18.190 --> 37:19.360
this is my karma.

37:24.920 --> 37:25.630
Mr. Lu,

37:27.110 --> 37:29.110
do you have any unfulfilled wishes?

37:32.400 --> 37:33.130
As your wife,

37:33.760 --> 37:35.620
is there anything I can do for you?

37:42.640 --> 37:44.900
There's a pot of flowers
under the corridor of my house.

37:44.900 --> 37:45.950
If it's okay,

37:46.220 --> 37:47.550
please take it with you.

37:47.560 --> 37:48.620
Give it some water.

37:48.850 --> 37:50.310
Don't let it wither or die.

37:50.480 --> 37:50.960
I will.

37:51.750 --> 37:53.150
I'll take good care of it.

39:06.230 --> 39:06.840
Stay back!

39:08.960 --> 39:09.840
Who are you?

39:10.530 --> 39:12.100
[Lu Jiujiu, Lu Xiaodao]

39:14.230 --> 39:15.490
Don't come any closer!

39:29.030 --> 39:29.590
Chubby?

39:29.930 --> 39:31.130
What brings you here?

39:32.510 --> 39:33.320
My wife

39:33.440 --> 39:35.110
heard that you're leaving Wei County.

39:35.110 --> 39:35.670
She prepared

39:35.670 --> 39:37.100
some pastries specifically for you

39:37.100 --> 39:38.360
to eat on your journey.

39:42.230 --> 39:43.400
Please pass on my gratitude to your wife.

39:43.400 --> 39:44.260
It tastes good.

39:45.320 --> 39:46.450
Where have you been?

39:48.360 --> 39:50.020
I've been to the Lu's Mansion.

39:50.590 --> 39:51.590
The Lu's Mansion?

39:52.160 --> 39:53.160
Lu Huai's house?

39:54.670 --> 39:56.130
What were you doing there?

39:56.320 --> 39:57.580
Do you really know him?

39:58.550 --> 39:59.760
It's a long story.

40:00.510 --> 40:02.170
You know a bit of my situation.

40:03.190 --> 40:04.390
Do you remember that?

40:04.920 --> 40:07.580
Since birth, I've been told
I have a cursed fate,

40:07.600 --> 40:08.360
a fate of widowhood

40:08.360 --> 40:09.800
that's bound to bring misfortune
to my husband.

40:08.410 --> 40:10.330
[Xin's Mansion]

40:17.150 --> 40:19.090
[Song Qingbao,
Head Clerk of the Central Secretariat]

40:28.380 --> 40:29.090
Lu Huai,

40:29.590 --> 40:31.120
your execution is in 2 days.

40:31.810 --> 40:32.470
Although your case

40:32.470 --> 40:34.000
was handled
by the Court of Judicial Review,

40:34.000 --> 40:35.660
and it's already set in stone,

40:35.960 --> 40:37.290
according to the rules,

40:37.480 --> 40:39.010
I still should ask you this.

40:39.510 --> 40:40.230
Lord Lu,

40:40.800 --> 40:42.550
do you want to declare any grievances

40:42.550 --> 40:43.550
or challenge the verdict?
